recent_articles.title: Chinese tech stocks soar in 2025 while US giants stall
recent_articles.summary:
US tech giants may be treading water in 2025, but Chinese tech stocks are up nearly 20% this year.

Morning Brief: Market Sunrise host Ramzan Karmali breaks down what’s behind the rally in China and whether investors should rethink their bet on the Magnificent Seven — the group of tech stocks comprised of Alphabet (GOOG, GOOGL), Apple (AAPL), Nvidia (NVDA), Tesla (TSLA), Amazon, Meta Platforms (META), and Microsoft (MSFT).

To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Morning Brief: Market Sunrise here.

recent_articles.title: Nvidia's market dominance leaves it with 'only one way to go'
recent_articles.summary:
Nvidia (NVDA) is dominating the artificial intelligence (AI) chip market, but its lead could shrink as rivals ramp up.

Gil Luria, D.A. Davidson head of technology research, joins Market Domination to explain how players like Advanced Micro Devices (AMD), Broadcom (AVGO), and Huawei are positioned to chip away at Nvidia's market share.
